===============================================================================
To generate sample application executable
===============================================================================
For Ubuntu Linux, run the command:
make TARGET_PLATFORM=LINUX_ZIP2 [DEBUG=1] [SHARED=1]    #build either debug or release version and shared or static application with 
                                                        #default to release and static application
**NOTE: arguments in [] are optional.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
For BeagleBone Black platform, run the command:
make TARGET_PLATFORM=BEAGLEBONE_ZIP2 [DEBUG=1] [SHARED=1]    #build either debug or release version and shared or static application with 
                                                             #default to release and static application
**NOTE: arguments in [] are optional.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
For Raspberry Pi platform, run the command:
make TARGET_PLATFORM=RASPBERRY_ZIP2 [DEBUG=1] [SHARED=1]    #build either debug or release version and shared or static application with 
                                                            #default to release and static application
**NOTE: arguments in [] are optional.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
For MAC OS X platform [EXPERIMENTAL, UNSUPPORTED], run the command:
make TARGET_PLATFORM=OSX_ZIP2

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
For Sigma SMP86XX Tangox platform [EXPERIMENTAL, UNSUPPORTED], run the command:
make TARGET_PLATFORM=SIGMA_ZIP2

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
For SMP8756 Vantage platform [EXPERIMENTAL, UNSUPPORTED], run the command:
make TARGET_PLATFORM=VANTAGE_ZIP2

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
For Android platform [EXPERIMENTAL, UNSUPPORTED], run the command:
make TARGET_PLATFORM=ANDROID_ZIP2


===============================================================================
To enable debug information, add "DEBUG=1" at build time
===============================================================================
Example:
make DEBUG=1
make TARGET_PLATFORM=LINUX_ZIP2 DEBUG=1

===============================================================================
To install binaries and configuration files to "install" sub-directory
===============================================================================
make install_all

===============================================================================
To install binaries only to "install" sub-directory
===============================================================================
make install_bin

